Indicators.Name: Tfirst
Indicators.Description: The first measured time for a given test case.

Indicators.Name: Tall
Indicators.Description: All measured times for a given test case.

Indicators.Name: Tmin
Indicators.Description: The minimal measured times for a given test case.

Indicators.Name: Tavg
Indicators.Description: The average of all measured times for a given test case.

Indicators.Name: Tsum
Indicators.Description: The sum of all measured times for a given test case.

Indicators.Name: Check
Indicators.Description: This indicator checks the correctness of the algorithm by comparing the expected output with the result of the algorithm and returns 'OK' if they are equal, or 'NOK' if they differ.
